@startuml
title Profile Update And Photo Management

actor Student
participant "Profile Page" as ProfilePage
participant "Profile Update Action" as ProfileAction
participant "Delete Photo Action" as PhotoDelete
participant "Bootstrap" as Bootstrap
database "MySQL DB\netudiant" as DB

Student -> ProfilePage: Open profile page
ProfilePage -> DB: Load student profile and photo data
DB --> ProfilePage: Current profile information

alt Update profile
    Student -> ProfileAction: Submit names, language,\noptional image
    ProfileAction -> Bootstrap: Validate authenticated request
    ProfileAction -> DB: UPDATE text fields\nand preferred language
    opt New image uploaded
        ProfileAction -> DB: UPDATE binary image data\nand MIME type
    end
    ProfileAction --> ProfilePage: Redirect back
else Delete photo
    Student -> PhotoDelete: Request photo deletion
    PhotoDelete -> DB: Set photo columns to NULL
    PhotoDelete --> ProfilePage: Redirect back
end

@enduml
